  "title": "Account Executive | Anchor Operator Preschool",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Execute daily financial operations, including processing centre collection summaries, student refunds, and relevant reconciliations in the internal system.</li>\n  <li>Facilitate the monthly accounting close by preparing necessary journal entries and generating detailed audit schedules.</li>\n  <li>Compile and analyze financial data for the preparation of monthly management reports, quarterly GST returns, and annual audit and tax documentation.</li>\n  <li>Generate additional financial reports to support half-year reviews, strategic business planning, and the annual budgeting process</li>\n  <li>Ensure financial integrity by performing regular bank reconciliations and maintaining accurate project accounting records.</li>\n  <li>Serve as a key liaison for external auditors during the annual field audit and assist in resolving annual tax queries.</li>\n  <li>Support strategic initiatives by inputting budgets for the new financial year and providing data-driven insights.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma/Degree in Finance/Accountancy/Banking or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Min 5 years of experience in Accounting settings</li>\n  <li>Working Hours: Weekdays</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out Aber Care Website for more details</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants please email your detailed resume to career@abercare.sg</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504|</p>",
