    "description": "<p>We Connect Opportunities to People<br>\n<br>\nAber Care is a recruitment agency specializing in connecting talented professionals with meaningful career opportunities in both healthcare and early childhood education.<br>\n<br>\nIn healthcare, our years of experience in the industry have given us deep insights into its manpower needs. We support hospitals, community hospitals, nursing homes, hospices, and senior care centers by placing skilled professionals such as staff nurses, nursing aides, nurse managers, healthcare assistants, and live-in caregivers. Beyond full-time and locum employment, we also provide foreign healthcare placement to ensure a strong and sustainable workforce.<br>\n<br>\nIn early childhood education, we partner with preschools to recruit dedicated educators, including preschool teachers, assistant teachers, and allied infant educarers, ensuring a nurturing learning environment for young children.<br>\n<br>\nWith expertise in both healthcare and education, we are committed to matching passionate professionals with rewarding careers while helping organizations build strong, dedicated teams in these essential fields.</p>\n<p>EA Licence No. 18C9070</p>",
